ration%2C%20we%20have%20about%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20Brownback%20told%20BI%2C%20referencing%20the%20Barclays%20Bloomberg%20Aggregate%20Bond%20Index.%20%26quot%3BWe%20hold%20about%2070%25%20of%20our%20duration%20five%20years%20and%20shorter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20duration.%20To%20generate%20the%206.4%25%20yield%2C%20Brownback%20tries%20to%20mix%20up%20the%20perfect%20cocktail%20of%20riskier%20assets%20with%20safer%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%2028%25%20of%20the%20fund%20is%20in%20commercial%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20asset-backed%20securities%2C%20collateralized%20loan%20obligations%2C%20and%20non-agency%20mortgages%2C%20he%20said.%20By%20diversifying%20these%20riskier%20assets%20with%20higher-quality%20AAA%20securitized%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20both%20higher-%20and%20lower-quality%20corporate%20credit%2C%20you%20get%20a%20robust%20return%2C%20Brownback%20said.%20AAA-rated%20credit%20is%20the%20highest%20class%20of%20investment-grade%20bonds%2C%20meaning%20the%20assets%20have%20the%20lowest%20risk%20levels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20the%20real%20sweet%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20Brownback%20said%20of%20the%20mix.%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20we're%20owning%20that%20in%20a%20diversified%20way%2C%20that's%20about%20the%20highest%20Sharpe%20Ratio%20that%20exists%20in%20markets%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referencing%20the%20risk-to-reward%20ratio.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20emphasis%20on%20diversification%2C%20Brownback%20said%20he's%20not%20worried%20about%20an%20impending%20economic%20downturn%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fear%20that%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-selloff-market-value-5-trump-trade-war-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eroiled%20markets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20lately%20as%20Presi