5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20white-collar%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20quality-of-life%20negatives%20for%20those%20they%20fly%20over%20are%20remarkably%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20down%20at%20the%20tiny%20skyscrapers%20from%20my%20seat%20next%20to%20the%20pilot%2C%20I%20was%20reminded%20of%20the%20similarly%20beautiful%20day%20in%20late%20September%20I'd%20spent%20picnicking%20on%20Governors%20Island%20off%20Lower%20Manhattan.%20What%20struck%20me%20then%20%E2%80%94%20and%20helped%20inspire%20my%20obsession%20with%20the%20helicopter%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20was%20how%20difficult%20it%20was%20to%20enjoy%20the%20idyllic%20car-free%20oasis%20with%20the%20near-constant%20chop-chop%20of%20helicopters%20overhead.%20Like%20many%20of%20the%20city's%20waterfront%20parks%2C%20the%20island%20has%20become%20what%20one%20anti-helicopter%20advocate%20told%20me%20is%20%26quot%3Bground%20zero%26quot%3B%20for%20chopper%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3E%20%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fdhg2o%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22NYC%20helicopter%20noise%20complaints%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22451%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20helicopter%20industry%20point%20to%20the%20safety%20hazards%20of%20congested%20skies%20and%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20the%20fuel-spewing%20machines.%20But%20the%20window-rattling%20racket%20they%20make%20tops%20the%20list%20of%20concerns.%20Loud%2C%20disruptive%20noise%20can%20have%20a%20range%20of%20physical%20and%20mental%20effects%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20raising%20the%20biomarkers%20for%20stress%20to%20changing%20how%20people's%20hearts%20and%20metabolisms%20work%2C%20and%20reducing%20people's%20lifespan%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20Shapiro%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20biology%20and%20society%20at%20UCLA%20who%20studies%20the%20health%20impacts%20of%20helicopter%20policing%2C%20told%20me.%20One%202017%20study%20linked%20aviation%20noise%20to%20disrupted%20sleep%2C%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20and%20lower%20academic%20performance%20among%20kids.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperson-under-flight-path-made-20k-complaints-noise-pollution-aircraft-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAircraft%20noise%20is%20especially%20annoying%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it's%20both%20loud%20and%20intermittent%2C%20Shapiro%20told%20me.%20Helicopters%20fly%20lower%20than%20planes%20and%20have%20the%20least%20regulated%20traffic%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChopper%20noise%20doesn't%20affect%20everyone%20the%20same%20way.%20People%20who've%20lived%20in%20war-torn%20or%20hyper-policed%20areas%20might%20have%20a%20more%20acute%20mental%20or%20physical%20reaction.%20%26quot%3BDifferent%20populations%20might%20feel%20stalked%20or%20harassed%20by%20that%20noise%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20culturally%20and%20historically%20informed%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20policing%2C%20the%20noise%20is%20often%20the%20point.%20Beginning%20during%20the%201965%20Watts%20riots%2C%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Police%20Department%20pioneered%20the%20use%20of%20helicopters%20to%20patrol%20neighborhoods.%20Flying%20low%2C%20sometimes%20using%20spotlights%2C%20most%20of%20the%20flights%20were%20used%20to%20deter%20crime%20rather%20than%20respond%20to%20emergencies.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sonic%20impacts%20are%20intended%20and%20part%20of%20its%20hypothesized%20efficacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20seeing%20the%20helicopter%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20helicopter%20seeing%20what's%20happening%20on%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%20A%202023%20audit%20found%20the%20LAPD's%20helicopter%20program%20costs%20about%20%2447%20million%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20the%20budgets%20of%2014%20city%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20found%20%26quot%3Blittle%20evidence%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20reduced%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Yorkers%20have%20long%20made%20a%20stink%20about%20helicopters%20over%20their%20streets.%20Mayor%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-keeps-his-stuff-after-mystery-deal-ga-election-workers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Rudy%20Giuliani%3C%2Fa%3E%20closed%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20heliports%20in%201997%20under%20pressure%20from%20incensed%20residents.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Council%20came%20close%20to%20shutting%20down%20two%20of%20the%20city's%20heliports%2C%20but%20Mayor%20Bill%20de%20Blasio%20settled%20on%20a%20compromise%20that%20halved%20the%20number%20of%20tourist%20flights%20that%20originate%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20from%2060%2C000%20flights%20a%20year%20to%2030%2C000.%20Since%20then%2C%20New%20Jersey%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20helicopter%20tour%20operators%2C%20which%20fly%20an%20unknown%20number%20of%20choppers%20over%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%2C%20Central%20Park%2C%20and%20everywhere%20in%20between%2C%20unrestricted%20by%20the%20city's%20regulations.%20The%20New%20York%20City%20Council%20analysis%20of%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguy-took-helicopter-jfk-catch-budget-flight-to-london-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelicopter%20traffic%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20number%20of%20tourist%20choppers%20in%20city%20airspace%20that%20originated%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20Westchester%20County%20was%20about%20the%20same%20as%20the%20number%20launching%20from%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Elstein%20began%20noticing%20an%20uptick%20in%20helicopters%20flying%20over%20her%20Upper%20West%20Side%20apartment%20and%20over%20Central%20Park%20in%20summer%202019.%20When%20she%20found%20out%20many%20were%20doors-off%2C%20shoe-selfie%20tourist%20choppers%2C%20she%20was%20incensed.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20insane%20that%20this%20is%20even%20allowed%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20we're%20also%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20city%20and%20with%20some%20of%20the%20busiest%20skies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20So%20Elstein%20decided%20to%20help%20revive%20Stop%20the%20Chop%20NY%2FNJ%2C%20a%20group%20pushing%20for%20much%20stricter%20regulation%20of%20nonessential%20choppers.%20The%20group%20has%20some%20high-profile%20supporters%2C%20including%20members%20of%20Congress%20and%20local%20elected%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20city%20controls%20what%20happens%20at%20its%20heliports%2C%20only%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20specifically%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-upgrades-air-safety-dc-crash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Aviation%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20controls%20New%20York%20City's%20airspace.%20New%20York%20Reps.%20Jerry%20Nadler%2C%20Carolyn%20Maloney%2C%20and%20Nydia%20Vel%C3%A1zquez%20have%20introduced%20federal%20legislation%20to%20ban%20nonessential%20choppers%20over%20the%20city.%20Some%20local%20lawmakers%20support%20the%20federal%20ban%20and%20want%20to%20see%20the%20city%20government%20end%20tourist%20and%20commuter%20flights%20from%20city-owned%20and%20operated%20heliports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20no%20reason%20that%20we%20should%20have%20city-owned%20helipads%20to%20fly%20the%20Uber%20elite%20out%20to%20JFK%20or%20the%20Hamptons%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20well-being%20of%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Lincoln%20Restler%2C%20a%20Brooklyn%20City%20council%20member%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20precedent%20for%20regulating%20or%20banning%20helicopter%20traffic.%20There%20are%20no-fly%20zones%20above%20some%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20prized%20monuments%20%E2%80%94%20the%20White%20House%20and%20the%20US%20Capitol%20and%2C%20naturally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-kid-problem-cable-tv-decline-disney-channel-watching-youtube-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Disney%20Land.%20Some%20major%20cities%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Paris%2C%20have%20also%20basically%20banned%20nonessential%20chopper%20flights.%20And%20several%20European%20countries%20have%20ended%20short-haul%20plane%20flights%20to%20help%20curb%20carbon%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City's%20Economic%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20which%20runs%20two%20of%20the%20three%20public%20heliports%2C%20has%20resisted%20efforts%20to%20further%20crack%20down%20on%20tourist%20flights%20in%20the%20city%2C%20citing%20the%20tourism%20dollars%20it%20brings%20in.%20Restler%20told%20me%20he%20doubts%20EDC's%20defense%20of%20helicopter%20tourism%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20farcical%26quot%3B%20and%20instead%20motivated%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20the%20wealthiest%20New%20Yorkers%20happy.%20For%20all%20the%20headache%2C%20the%20city-owned%20heliports%20only%20bring%20in%20about%20%243%20million%20a%20year%20in%20revenue%2C%20Anton%20Fredriksson%2C%20EDC's%20director%20of%20aviation%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEssential%20flights%26quot%3B%20are%20also%20a%20growing%20part%20of%20the%20noise%20problem.%20Under%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%2C%20the%20New%20York%20police%20department's%20use%20of%20law%20enforcement%20choppers%20has%20risen%20dramatically.%20A%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fgraphics%2F2024-nyc-police-helicopter-flights%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBloomberg%20investigation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20force's%20helicopters%20spent%2060%25%20more%20time%20in%20the%20air%20in%202023%20than%20in%20the%20previous%20four%20years.%20The%20NYPD's%20spending%20on%20the%20helicopter%20program%20more%20than%20doubled%20between%20fiscal%20year%202021%20and%202023%20to%20%2412.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20helicopter%20industry%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20a%20major%20transformation.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20FAA%20published%20a%20report%20outlining%20its%20path%20to%20approving%20the%20first%20so-called%20electric%20vertical%20takeoff%20and%20landing%2C%20or%20eVTOL%2C%20aircraft%20for%20commercial%20flight%20by%202025%20%E2%80%94%20and%20widespread%20use%20by%202028.%20These%20machines%20are%20basically%20electric%20versions%20of%20helicopters%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20been%20hyped%20by%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-agency-tech-buzzword-silicon-valley-hiring-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20for%20years.%20Some%20chopper%20services%2C%20including%20Blade%2C%20want%20them%20to%20replace%20their%20use%20of%20combustion-engine%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20a%20really%20exciting%20new%20age%20where%20instead%20of%20moving%20around%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20we're%20able%20to%20move%20around%20in%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20Allison%2C%20the%20chief%20product%20officer%20of%20one%20California-based%20eVTOL%20company%2C%20Joby%20Aviation%2C%20told%20me.%20Joby%20has%20partnered%20with%20Uber%2C%20Delta%2C%20Toyota%2C%20and%20the%20US%20government%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20launch%20its%20air%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-robotaxi-service-rides-austin-june-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaxi%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Uber%20Black%20prices%20and%20eventually%20hopes%20to%20bring%20them%20closer%20to%20UberX%20prices.%20It's%20not%20clear%20when%20they'll%20get%20final%20certification%20from%20the%20FAA%20to%20start%20ferrying%20people%20around%20the%20US%2C%20but%20they're%20undergoing%20approval%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20resisting%20the%20regulation%20of%20traditional%20helicopters%20for%20decades%2C%20New%20York%20leaders%20are%20embracing%20the%20electric%20rotor%20industry%20with%20open%20arms%20as%20the%20solution%20to%20noise%20and%20air%20pollution.%20Some%20support%20lifting%20caps%20on%20flights%20if%20they're%20electric.%20The%20mayor%20and%20EDC%20invited%20Joby%20and%20a%20German%20company%20to%20show%20off%20their%20machines%20in%20a%20test%20flight%20in%20downtown%20Manhattan%20in%20late%202023.%20Adams%20predicted%20at%20the%20event%20that%20%26quot%3Bwithin%20our%20lifetime%2C%20many%20of%20you%20are%20going%20to%20own%20your%20own%20personal%20electric%20helicopter.%26quot%3B%20There%20are%20some%20clear%20upsides%20to%20the%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20eVTOLs%20are%20much%20quieter%20than%20combustion-engine%20helicopters%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20spew%20jet%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20city%20lawmakers%20who've%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20helicopter%20industry%20are%20welcoming%20their%20electric%20counterparts.%20%26quot%3BThe%20future%20of%20electric%20air%20taxi%20travel%20represents%20innovation%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20expanded%20transportation%20options%20for%20our%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Amanda%20Far%C3%ADas%2C%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Council%20majority%20leader%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestler%20is%20more%20cautious.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20we%20actually%20experience%20how%20they%20work%20in%20practice%20and%20what%20impacts%20they%20have%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20kind%20of%20what%20regulatory%20structure%20we%20need%20to%20protect%20the%20health%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20safety%20of%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Blade%20announced%20it's%20expanding%20its%20JFK%20flight%20offerings%20to%20the%20downtown%20Manhattan%20heliport%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20help%20the%20heliport's%20new%20operator%20%26quot%3Bgather%20data%20on%20consumer%20demand%2C%20flier%20experience%2C%20and%20logistics%26quot%3B%20and%20transition%20to%20eVTOLs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20we're%20hurtling%20toward%20a%20future%20of%20highways%20in%20the%20sky%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20already%20there%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-london-lived-both-cities-prefer-british-capital-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENYC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20it's%20not%20clear%20it's%20one%20that%20appeals%20to%20the%20average%20city%20dweller.%20It%20might%20warrant%20asking%20the%20question%3A%20Do%20we%20want%20the%201%25%20taking%20over%20the%20skies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Feliza-relman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EEliza%20Relman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20policy%20correspondent%20focused%20on%20housing%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20on%20Insider's%20economy%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-new-york-city-helicopter-commute-avoid-cars-traffic-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742803921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67dd98bc63d72727e197ebf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-new-york-city-helicopter-commute-avoid-cars-traffic-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20took%20a%20helicopter%20from%20midtown%20Manhattan%20to%20JFK%20airport%20in%209%20minutes.%20I%20may%20never%20take%20an%20Uber%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22erelman%40businessinsider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-new-york-city-helicopter-commute-avoid-cars-traffic-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%203.4%20L%20cr%20hit%20to%20market%20cap!%20Adani%20stocks%20plunge%20up%20to%2048%25%20so%20far%20in%20FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742803484000%2C%