recorded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20while%20he%20is%20not%20against%20comedy%2C%20disrespecting%20someone%20is%20not%20okay.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20low-level%20comedy%20and%20disrespecting%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20not%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20%26quot%3Bgaddar%26quot%3B%20jab%20at%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20should%20that%20Maharashtra%20people%20showed%20who%20is%20'gaddar'%20(traitor)%20and%20who%20is%20not%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%20People%20have%20decided%20to%20who%20has%20the%20legacy%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20the%20Kunal%20Kamra%20should%20apologise%20for%20his%20remarks%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20legitimise%20your%20fault%20by%20showing%20such%20Constitution.%20The%20Constitution%20gives%20us%20freedom%20but%20it%20is%20not%20absolute%2C%20you%20cannot%20encroach%20on%20others'%20freedom.%20There%20are%20limitations%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20said%20everyone%20should%20speak%20responsibly%20so%20that%20police%20do%20not%20need%20to%20intervene.%C2%A0%26quot%3BNo%20one%20should%20go%20beyond%20the%20law%20and%20the%20Constitution.%20One%20should%20speak%20within%20limits.%20Differences%20of%20opinion%20may%20exist%2C%20but%20care%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20police%20department%20does%20not%20have%20to%20intervene%20due%20to%20their%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20told%20the%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20workers%20yesterday%20went%20on%20the%20rampage%20at%20Mumbai's%20Habitat%20studio%20to%20protest%20against%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20remarks%20at%20a%20show%20recorded%20about%20a%20month%20back.%20Visuals%20showed%20Sena%20workers%20swinging%20chairs%20and%20damaging%20cameras%2C%20lights%20and%20speakers%20at%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Kamra%20targeted%20Eknath%20Shinde%20with%20a%20parody%20version%20of%20'Bholi%20Si%20Surat'%2C%20a%20popular%20song%20from%20the%201997%20blockbuster%20Dil%20To%20Pagal%20Hai.%20He%20used%20the%20'gaddar'%20(traitor)%20jibe%20against%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20who%20led%20a%20rebellion%20against%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20in%202022%2C%20bringing%20down%20his%20government%20and%20splitting%20the%20party.%20Multiple%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20comic%2C%20including%20one%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20studio%2C%20which%20is%20a%20preferred%20venue%20for%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20shut%20down%20for%20now.%20In%20a%20statement%20posted%20on%20its%20official%20Instagram%20handle%2C%20The%20Habitat%20said%20it%20has%20decided%20to%20shut%20down%20%26quot%3Btill%20we%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20free%20expression%20without%20putting%20ourselves%20and%20our%20property%20in%20jeopardy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shocked%2C%20worried%20and%20extremely%20broken%20by%20the%20recent%20acts%20of%20vandalism%20targeting%20us.%20Artists%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20their%20views%20and%20creative%20choices.%20We%20have%20never%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20content%20performed%20by%20any%20Artist%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20events%20have%20made%20us%20rethink%20about%20how%20we%20get%20blamed%20and%20targeted%20every%20time%20almost%20like%20we%20are%20a%20proxy%20for%20the%20performer%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20studio%20was%20in%20the%20news%20earlier%20for%20the%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20episode%20during%20which%20YouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shutting%20down%20till%20we%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20free%20expression%20without%20putting%20ourselves%20and%20our%20property%20in%20jeopardy.%20We%20invite%20all%20artists%2C%20audience%20and%20stakeholders%20to%20discuss%20and%20share%20their%20views%20freely%20and%20request%20your%20guidance%20so%20that%20we%20also%20respect%20the%20performers'%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20studio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20action%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20from%20its%20arch-rival%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20Targeting%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20MLA%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Bonly%20an%20insecure%20coward%20would%20react%20to%20a%20song%20by%20someone%26quot%3B.%20He%20has%20also%20questioned%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20said%20Mr%20Shinde%20was%20not%20named%20in%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20joke.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20vandalism%20shows%20that%20it%20hurt%20them%20and%20that%20there%20is%20truth%20in%20the%20joke.%20What%20kind%20of%20intolerance%20is%20this%3F%20If%20you%20don't%20like%20something%2C%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik%2C%20who%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%2C%20said%20he%20is%20a%20minister%20and%20does%20not%20support%20vandalism.%20%26quot%3BBut%20objectionable%20remarks%20were%20made%20against%20our%20leader.%20If%20our%20leader%20is%20targeted%2C%20we%20won't%20spare%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20studio%20hosting%20the%20show%20was%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B.%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Milind%20Deora%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20Opposition%20and%20said%20mocking%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bself-made%20leader%26quot%3B%2C%20reeks%20of%20%26quot%3Bclassist%20arrogance%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20rejecting%20entitled%20monarchs%20%26amp%3B%20their%20bootlicking%20ecosystem%20that%20pretends%20to%20champion%20meritocracy%20%26amp%3B%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20have%20registered%20two%20cases%20in%20this%20connection%3A%20one%20against%20Kunal%20Kamra%20for%20his%20remarks%20and%20another%20against%20Sena%20workers%20for%20the%20vandalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742797320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fkehjsp68_kunal-kamra-fadnavis-reax_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-kunal-kamra-jibe-at-eknath-shinde-ajit-pawar-says-one-should-speak-within-their-rights-7996230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Row%20Over%20Kunal%20Kamra%20Jibe%20At%20Eknath%20Shinde%3A%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Says%20One%20Should%20Speak%20Within%20Their%20Rights%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frow-over-kunal-kamra-jibe-at-eknath-shinde-ajit-pawar-says-one-should-speak-within-their-rights-7996230%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20Mumbai%20police%20book%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%20over%20defamatory%20remarks%20on%20Shinde%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742797032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-kunal-kamra-rahul-gandhi-live-updates-encounter-india-world-news-2025-0324-125032400090_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latest%20news%20updates%3A%20Catch%20all%20the%20live%20news%20updates%20from%20around%20the%20world%20here%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fshiv-sena-kunal-kamra-rahul-gandhi-live-updates-encounter-india-world-news-2025-0324-125032400090_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bank%20strike%3A%20Are%20banks%20closed%20on%20March%2024%20and%2025%20nationwide%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742796982000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%