n%20unusual%20request%20from%20Ukrainians%20in%20the%20trenches.%20They%20needed%20nets%20%E2%80%94%20thick%20ones%20strong%20enough%20to%20stop%20the%20munition-laden%20drones%20that%20have%20become%20the%20battlefield's%20leading%20killer.%20Soldiers%20were%20draping%20them%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-new-defenses-harder-for-russia-to-gain-ground-expert-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efortified%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20combat%20vehicles%20as%20a%20final%20defense%2C%20and%20Futtrup%20heard%20they%20were%20saving%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20write%20to%20me%20that%20they%20want%20more%20because%2C%20without%20this%2C%20all%20other%20donations%20are%20worthless%2C%26quot%3B%20Futtrup%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThybor%C3%B8n%2C%20a%20fishing%20village%20of%20some%202%2C000%20people%20in%20Jutland%2C%20just%20happened%20to%20have%20450%20tons%20of%20those%20nets%20sitting%20unused%20at%20the%20harbor.%20These%20were%20trawling%20nets%2C%20made%20of%20nylon%20fibers%20up%20to%20four%20millimeters%20thick%20for%20hauling%20hundreds%20of%20fish%20at%20a%20time%20from%20the%20deep%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuttrup%20found%20Thybor%C3%B8n's%20fishermen%20on%20Facebook%20and%20asked%20if%20they%20were%20open%20to%20making%20a%20donation.%20They%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20nets%20are%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20being%20used%20to%20snag%20Russian%20drones%20similar%20to%20insects%20on%20flypaper.%20They're%20just%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20what%20Futtrup%20and%20other%20volunteers%20hope%20will%20be%20a%20total%20of%202.1%20million%20pounds%20of%20Danish%20commercial%20nets%20%E2%80%94%20left%20over%20from%20Brexit%20fishing%20disputes%20%E2%80%94%20lining%20Ukrainian%20fortifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20munitions%20are%20caught%20in%20nets%20deployed%20by%20Ukrainians%20on%20fortified%20positions.%5C%22%20charse