upport-soldiers-prep-for-refugees-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimarily%20to%20provide%20camouflage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Ardashyn%20said%2C%20there's%20been%20an%20increased%20demand%20for%20heavy-duty%20nets%20as%20troops%20realized%20they%20can%20be%20a%20reliable%20option%20to%20counter%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems.%20The%20need%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20growing%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unjammable-fiber-optic-drone-keep-pace-russia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber-optic%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20bypass%20electronic%20jamming%20and%20have%20to%20be%20blocked%20or%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20talking%20about%20big%20nets%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardashyn%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20those%20that%20people%20use%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20the%20really%20big%20ones%2C%20like%20from%20ships.%20The%20material%20is%20strong%20enough%20that%20it%20can%20handle%20a%20drone%20falling%20from%20the%20sky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20units%20have%20started%20draping%20thick%20nets%20on%20the%20tree%20lines%20along%20supply%20routes%20to%20hinder%20ambushes%20from%20skilled%20Russian%20drone%20pilots.%20Others%20have%20shrouded%20their%20fortified%20positions%20completely%20in%20netting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow's%20troops%20are%20using%20them%20too%2C%20said%20Federico%20Borsari%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%20who%20studies%20drone%20warfare%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russians%20are%20using%20nets%20to%20cover%20entire%20roads%20and%20protect%20their%20logistics%20from%20Ukrainian%20first-person%20view%20UAVs%2C%20with%20mixed%20results%20depending%20on%20the%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20But%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20either%20side%20will%20have%20enough%20time%20or%20resources%20to%20cover%20their%20entire%20rear%20with%20nets%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroops%20also%20use%20them%20to%20protect%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20relying%20on%20a%20combination%20of%20nets%20and%20metal%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-shows-tanks-need-cages-protect-from-exploding-drones-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonce%20mocked%20as%20%26quot%3Bcope%20cages%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20lower%20the%20chances%20of%20direct%20impact%20from%20a%20drone.%20Even%20a%20foot%20or%20two%20distance%20from%20a%20vehicle's%20armored%20body%20can%20reduce%20a%20drone's%20explosive%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20nets%20needed%20is%20increasing%20exponentially%2C%26quot%3B%20Ardashyn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20weapons%20are%20seen%20covered%20in%20metal%20frames%20with%20nets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67da5e2cb8b41a9673fb0c77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainians%20have%20been%20using%20nets%20to%20shield%20their%20armored%20vehicles%20and%20guns%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Carl%20Futtrup%20and%20Mykhaylo%20Ardashyn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2061ea5-0481-4f7f-b683-35480b07325a%5C%22%3EBrexit's%20loss%2C%20Ukraine's%20gain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Denmark%2C%20Futtrup%20has%20been%20contacting%20other%20local%20harbors%20and%20secured%20another%20600%20tons%20of%20trawl%20nets%20to%20send%20to%20Ukraine%20via%20truck.%20He's%20been%20speaking%20with%20Ukrainian%20media%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Kyiv%20Post%2C%20trying%20to%20raise%20funds%20from%20volunteers%20and%20the%20Danish%20government%20for%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20heavy%20expense%20for%20the%20gardener%2C%20with%20costs%20for%20the%20second%20shipment%20totaling%20about%2090%2C000%20euros.%20Futtrup%20estimates%20that%20each%20truck%20can%20carry%20up%20to%2020%20tons%20of%20nets%2C%20and%20each%20trip%20will%20cost%20about%203%2C000%20euros%2C%20or%20%243%2C200.%20A%20typical%20trawl%20net%20is%20about%201%2C300%20feet%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nets%20themselves%20are%20free.%20Carsten%20Bach%2C%20a%20parliament%20member%20of%20the%20Danish%20right-wing%20Liberal%20Alliance%20opposition%20party%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20most%20of%20the%20donated%20nets%20sat%20in%20storage%20for%20years%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrexit-deal-fishing-agreement-uk-services-eu-uk-johson-limbo-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrexit%20cut%20off%20British%20fishing%20waters%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Danish%20fishermen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fishing%20nets%20are%20seen%20heaped%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Denmark.%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20haul%20nets%20delivered%20by%20Futtrup%20and%20other%20volunteers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67da6192585f1dff88b28a6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20donated%20nets%20were%20sitting%20in%20harbors%20because%20Brexit%20prevented%20Danish%20fishermen%20from%20using%20them%20in%20British%20waters%2C%20Bach%20said.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Carl%20Futtrup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20fishermen%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20in%20these%20nets.%20It's%20quite%20a%20large%20investment%20for%20a%20small%20company%20or%20a%20single-person%20fisherman%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bach%2C%20who%20is%20his%20party's%20spokesman%20on%20both%20defense%20and%20food.%20The%20fishing%20industry%20contributes%20about%200.75%25%20of%20Denmark's%20GDP%2C%20but%20the%20country%20is%20the%20world's%20fifth%20largest%20exporter%20of%20fish%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBach%20said%20many%20fishermen%20chose%20to%20keep%20their%20nets%2C%20hoping%20that%20a%20new%20agreement%20with%20the%20UK%20could%20restore%20access%20to%20their%20old%20fishing%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Danish%20environmental%20laws%20require%20such%20equipment%20to%20be%20disposed%20of%20or%20recycled%20eventually.%20And%20Bach%20said%20fishermen%20typically%20must%20pay%20a%20large%20fee%20for%20this%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20politician%2C%20who%20is%20helping%20Futtrup%20submit%20a%20financing%20proposal%20to%20the%20Danish%20government%2C%20said%20it's%20therefore%20likely%20these%20trawl%20nets%20won't%20be%20a%20renewable%20resource%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20not%2C%20in%20the%20future%2C%20be%20as%20large%20a%20volume%20of%20fishing%20equipment%20like%20this%20for%20disposal%20in%20Denmark%2C%26quot%3B%20Bach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201795507-471a-4297-9997-418e529b6698%5C%22%3EDanish%20nets%20won't%20last%20forever%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Futtrup's%20nets%20are%20supplying%20at%20least%2013%20units%20on%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20said%20Bernard%20Christensen%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Swedish%20non-governmental%20organization%20Operation%20Change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20our%20main%20vein%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristensen%2C%20a%20Swede%20living%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20has%20been%20helping%20brigades%20find%20sources%20for%20heavy-duty%20nets.%20One%20brigade%20typically%20requests%20about%2050%20to%2080%20tons%20of%20netting%2C%20and%20they%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20procure%20locally%2C%20he%20said.%20Russian-controlled%20territory%20blocks%20much%20of%20Ukraine's%20access%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-navy-using-azov-sea-strike-ukraine-still-exposed-experts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlack%20Sea%20and%20the%20Sea%20of%20Azov.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20unit%20commander%20overseeing%20fortifications%20and%20mine-laying%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20direction%20told%20BI%20that%20his%20battalion%20needs%20about%20three%20truckloads%2C%20or%20roughly%2060%20tons%20of%20nets%2C%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20local%20sources%20for%20these%20nets%2C%20they%20can%20only%20be%20obtained%20from%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20commander%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20due%20to%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20his%20work.%20His%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20takes%20his%20men%20about%20three%20to%20four%20days%20to%20set%20up%20one%20truckload%2C%20often%20in%20miles-long%20%26quot%3Btunnels%26quot%3B%20of%20netting%20along%20roads%20to%20protect%20vehicles%20against%20drone%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20volunteer%20donations%2C%20there's%20barely%20enough%20to%20go%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20units%20desperately%20need%20these%20marine%20nets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20photos%20show%20Futtrup's%20fishing%20nets%20being%20loaded%20into%20a%20truck%20in%20Denmark%20and%20then%20unloaded%20in%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67da5eb5b8b41a9673fb0c78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20nets%20discovered%20by%20Futtrup%20are%20loaded%20by%20crane%20in%20Denmark%2C%20then%20trucked%20over%20to%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Carl%20Futtrup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20Futtrup's%20nets%20will%20eventually%20run%20out%2C%20and%20Christensen%20must%20search%20elsewhere%20soon.%20Operation%20Change%20is%20looking%20to%20acquire%20nets%20from%20organizations%20cleaning%20up%20the%20western%20Swedish%20coast%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Kavanagh%2C%20director%20of%20military%20analysis%20at%20the%20Washington-based%20think%20tank%20Defense%20Priorities%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Ukraine's%20demand%20for%20fishing%20nets%20is%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20fighting%20there%20has%20democratized%20modern%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20military%20and%20political%20leaders%20are%20always%20searching%20for%20the%20next%20best%20weapon%20or%20military%20system%2C%20the%20one%20platform%20that%20will%20give%20the%20United%20States%20insurmountable%20advantages%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20what%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20shown%20is%20that%20while%20these%20types%20of%20high-tech%20solutions%20to%20military%20challenges%20have%20their%20place%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-invasion-west-focused-too-much-weapon-quantity-over-numbers-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-tech%20and%20inexpensive%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20sometimes%20work%20just%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20advanced%20platforms%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20win%20a%20future%20war%2C%20since%20they%20might%20be%20defeated%20by%20a%20less%20capable%20adversary%20with%20a%20simple%20or%20cheap%20defense%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFishing%20nets%20might%20not%20be%20the%20right%20response%20for%20the%20US%20military%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%20and%20others%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20should%20spend%20more%20time%20exploring%20less%20advanced%20options%20rather%20than%20defaulting%20immediately%20to%20complex%20and%20bespoke%20designs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kavanagh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Futtrup%20said%20he's%20pouring%20his%20energy%20into%20securing%20the%20money%20to%20truck%20over%20the%20donated%20nets.%20He%20hopes%20to%20acquire%2050%2C000%20euros%20from%20Swedish%20and%20Danish%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20part%20of%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20only%201%2C250%20kilometers%20from%20Copenhagen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20there%20is%20demand%20for%20fishing%20nets%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20I%20will%20send%20them%2C%20until%20there%20is%20no%20more%20to%20be%20found%20in%20Denmark%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslation%20by%20Sofiia%20Meleshenko.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanish-fishing-village-ukraine-war-counter-drones-nets-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742795610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67da658769253ccddf99a644%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanish-fishing-village-ukraine-war-counter-drones-nets-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heavy-duty%20trawl%20nets%20have%20become%20a%20hot%20commodity%20among%20Ukrainian%20troops%20trying%20to%20counter%20fiber-optic%20drones%20and%20other%20munitions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanish-fishing-village-ukraine-war-counter-drones-nets-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NewJeans%20announce%20hiatus%20after%20setback%20in%20court%20battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742795585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7187%2Flive%2F1f35cae0-086a-11f0-97d3-37df2b293ed1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgr2vplwjeeo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20K-pop%20group%2C%20which%20now%20call%20themselves%20NJZ%2C%20announce%20a%20pause%20after%20debuting%20a%20new%20song.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgr2vplwjeeo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fw