pardy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shocked%2C%20worried%20and%20extremely%20broken%20by%20the%20recent%20acts%20of%20vandalism%20targeting%20us.%20Artists%20are%20solely%20responsible%20for%20their%20views%20and%20creative%20choices.%20We%20have%20never%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20content%20performed%20by%20any%20Artist%2C%20but%20the%20recent%20events%20have%20made%20us%20rethink%20about%20how%20we%20get%20blamed%20and%20targeted%20every%20time%20almost%20like%20we%20are%20a%20proxy%20for%20the%20performer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20studio%20was%20in%20the%20news%20earlier%20for%20the%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20episode%20during%20which%20YouTuber%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20shutting%20down%20till%20we%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20free%20expression%20without%20putting%20ourselves%20and%20our%20property%20in%20jeopardy.%20We%20invite%20all%20artists%2C%20audience%20and%20stakeholders%20to%20discuss%20and%20share%20their%20views%20freely%20and%20request%20your%20guidance%20so%20that%20we%20also%20respect%20the%20performers'%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20studio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20studio%20had%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20that%20it%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20making%20of%20Kunal%20Kamra's%20latest%20video%20and%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20endorse%20the%20views%20expressed%20by%20it%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20extend%20a%20sincere%20and%20heartfelt%20apology%20to%20all%20those%20hurt%20by%20this%20video%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said%20after%20a%20group%20of%20Sena%20workers%20entered%20the%20premises%20in%20Khar%20and%20damaged%20property%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20comic's%20remarks%20against%20Mr%20Shinde.%20Visuals%20showed%20Sena%20workers%20swinging%20chairs%20at%20cameras%2C%20lights%20and%20speakers%20at%20the%20studio.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Kunal%20Kamra%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20be%20outspoken%20in%20his%20comedy%20shows%20and%20political%20views%2C%20Kunal%20Kamra%20targeted%20Mr%20Shinde%20with%20a%20parody%20version%20of%20'Bholi%20Si%20Surat'%2C%20a%20popular%20song%20from%20the%201997%20blockbuster%20Dil%20To%20Pagal%20Hai.%20He%20used%20the%20'gaddar'%20(traitor)%20jibe%20against%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20who%20led%20a%20rebellion%20against%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20in%202022%2C%20bringing%20down%20his%20government%20and%20splitting%20the%20party.%20Multiple%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20comic%2C%20including%20one%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20minister%20Pratap%20Sarnaik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Political%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESena's%20vandalism%20at%20the%20studio%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MLA%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20said%20%26quot%3Bonly%20an%20insecure%20coward%20would%20react%20to%20a%20song%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20questioned%20the%20state's%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20under%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government.%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Milind%20Deora%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20Opposition%20and%20said%20mocking%20Mr%20Shinde%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bself-made%20leader%26quot%3B%2C%20reeks%20of%20%26quot%3Bclassist%20arrogance%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20rejecting%20entitled%20monarchs%20%26amp%3B%20their%20bootlicking%20ecosystem%20that%20pretends%20to%20champion%20meritocracy%20%26amp%3B%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742794800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fem528gi8_kamra-vandalism_650x400_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-studio-shutting-down-after-vandalism-by-shiv-sena-workers-over-kunal-kamra-show