22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20this%20week%2C%20Yisroel%20Liebb%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bvisibly%20enraged%26quot%3B%20pilot%20broke%20the%20lock%20on%20the%20restroom%20door%20and%20forced%20Liebb%20out%20while%20his%20pants%20were%20around%20his%20ankles%2C%20exposing%20his%20genitalia%20to%20other%20nearby%20passengers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiebb%20and%20another%20passenger%20he%20was%20traveling%20with%2C%20Jacob%20Sebbag%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Jewish%2C%20claim%20they%20suffered%20physical%20injuries%2C%20emotional%20distress%2C%20and%20discrimination%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20airline%20staff%20and%20federal%20agents%20on%20the%20flight%20from%20Tulum%2C%20Mexico%2C%20to%20Houston%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20events%20unfolded%20on%20January%2028%2C%202025%2C%20after%20a%20flight%20attendant%20woke%20Sebbag%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20check%20on%20Liebb%2C%20who%20had%20been%20in%20the%20bathroom%20for%20about%2020%20minutes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiebb%20responded%20that%20he%20was%20experiencing%20constipation%20and%20would%20exit%20shortly%2C%20but%20the%20pilot%20demanded%20he%20leave%20immediately%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20claim%20that%20after%20Liebb%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20restroom%2C%20the%20pilot%20%26quot%3Bproceeded%20to%20repeatedly%20push%26quot%3B%20them%20back%20to%20their%20seats%20while%20making%20discriminatory%20remarks%20about%20their%20Judaism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20arrival%20in%20Houston%2C%20agents%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%2C%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%2C%20and%20the%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%20boarded%20the%20plane%20and%20restrained%20Liebb%2C%20forced%20his%20arms%20behind%20his%20back%2C%20and%20handcuffed%20him%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20Sebbag%20was%20also%20detained%20after%20confirming%20that%20Liebb%20was%20in